Text: TuxesHey fellas A couple days left If you guys get this today Thursday and if you get a chance could you call the tux shop and go ahead and pay for your tuxes I am going to pick up all of the tuxes this afternoon and bring them out to the rehearsal tomorrow IF you are in town you can just go to the shop on Clybourn and pay for and pick up your tux otherwise if you could call and pay with a credit card it would make things a lot easier I will be going over there at or this afternoon If you could either call and pay for you tux or at least let me know that you are planning to pick it up tonight before Cellular Id really appreciate it Modern Tuxedo North Clybourn Chicago Hours PM Thanks guys Safe travels Jas Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at

tux pickupHey guys Less than two weeks now Just wanted to find out when everyone would be arriving they want us to pick up the tuxes and pay for everything on Thursday evening I know some of you wont be in until Friday so well work around that The shop is also in the city so we may have to try and move to one of the shops in the burbs if you all are headed out there Let me know when youll be available and Ill figure it out for the group Later Jason Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at

Fwd Hotel room updateThought some of you would be interested in this Get those reservations now Jas From alueb ReplyTo alueb To Jasons parents CC Jason Childers Subject Hotel room update Date Tue May I have been told by a few people that the Hyatt has no more rooms available for Saturday June nd According to the Hyatt there are still several rooms available and more can be reserved if needed Please call prior to May th to reserve your room The reservation number is and refer to the LuebberingChilders wedding The Fairfield Inn also had rooms available Their reservation number is Sorry for any inconvenience Please forward this to anyone who was having trouble reserving a room Thank you Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at

Wedding proofsPST Good morning everyone Just wanted to let you know that we finally have some of our proofs available online It isnt our whole book but it is a fair sample I think they got most of the pictures of you guys posted if you are interested in buying a print I believe you can order directly from the page If anyone wants to see more call Andrea or myself and we can help you out Steps for accessing the proofs are Point your browser to wwwelanphotographycom From the home page select Weddings From the Weddings page select Online Ordering This will open a new browser window to a list of weddings shot by our photographer Select the ChildersLuebbering wedding This will prompt you to enter a username and password Enter username childers password gnirebbeul Browse at will I believe there are three or four pages of proofs If you drill down on a picture you can order it there Let me know if you have any problems accessing this site Later Jason Get your FREE download of MSN Explorer at
